videos.headline: Diving TD catch puts UTSA up on Arizona State
videos.description: Texas San Antonio quarterback Dalton Sturm finds a diving JaBryce Taylor in the end zone for the score to give the Roadrunners an early 7-3 lead over Arizona State.

videos.headline: Arizona State stops UT San Antonio QB with hard hit
videos.description: Koron Crump run for 3 yds to the ArzSt 26

videos.headline: A. King punt for 49 yds,K. Ballage returns for -6 yds,K. Ballage fumbled, recovered by TexSA
videos.description: Andrew King punt for 49 yds , Kalen Ballage returns for a loss of 6 yards to the ArzSt 14 Kalen Ballage fumbled, recovered by TexSA

videos.headline: UTSA increases the lead with another diving TD catch
videos.description: After JaBryce Taylor scored earlier on a diving catch, Jalen Rhodes does the same, this time in the front corner of the end zone to increase UTSA's lead over Arizona State to 14-3.

videos.headline: M. Wilkins pass intercepted,N. Gaines return  for 0 yds
videos.description: Manny Wilkins pass intercepted Nate Gaines return for no gain to the TexSA 30

videos.headline: M. Wilkins pass,to C. Smith for 39 yds for a 1ST down
videos.description: Manny Wilkins pass complete to Cameron Smith for 39 yds to the ArzSt 48 for a 1ST down

videos.headline: Harry makes the nasty one-handed touchdown catch
videos.description: In the final seconds of the half, N'Keal Harry makes the incredible one-handed catch while falling down for an Arizona State touchdown to cut the Sun Devils' deficit to 14-12.

videos.headline: Jarveon Williams with the moves for a 48-yard gain
videos.description: Dalton Sturm pass complete to Jarveon Williams for 48 yards for a 1ST down

videos.headline: Dalton Sturm dives into the end zone for a 34-yard TD
videos.description: Dalton Sturm run for 34 yds for a TD (Victor Falcon KICK)

videos.headline: Arizona State's special teams turn the ball over for the second time
videos.description: Yannis Routsas punt for 35 yards, Gump Hayes returns for no gain to the Arizona State 24, Gump Hayes fumbled, recovered by UT San Antonio Aneas Henricks

videos.headline: Kalen Ballage fumbles the ball for Arizona State's third turnover of the night
videos.description: Kalen Ballage run for 6 yds to the UTSA 48 Kalen Ballage fumbled, recovered by Arizona State N'Keal Harry

videos.headline: Big play touchdown has Arizona State clawing back
videos.description: Trailing by 10 in the fourth quarter, Manny Wilkins connects with Frederick Gammage for a 45-yard touchdown to get Arizona State back in the game down 28-25.

videos.headline: Arizona State claws all the way back to take the lead with 3:15 left
videos.description: After trailing for most of the game, Kalen Ballage takes the snap and gets through the line for the touchdown to put Arizona State on top with 3:15 left in the game.
